  "Total number of messages sent by the account."

  "Total number of messages received by the account."
  messageReceivedCount: Int!
  "Collection of bridge messages related to the account, derived from the 'account' field."
  messages: [BridgeMessage!]! @derivedFrom(field: "account")
}"}
